summary: An ordinance accepting deeds from C. B. Thomas and Jane L. Thomas, his wife, Anne A. Stuart and B. F. Stuart, her husband, to the City of Seattle, executed on the 12th day of June, 1925; and from Anne A. Stuart and B. F. Stuart, her husband, to The City of Seattle, executed on the 27th day of November, 1925; and laying off Mead Street.
